- site_name = LinkedData.settings.ui_name
%p
  A new user account has been created on 
  %b #{site_name}.
%p
  Account details:
%div{style: "background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #{Notifier::PORTAL_COLOR}; margin: 20px 0;"}
  %p{style: "margin: 0 0 10px 0;"}
    %strong Username: 
    = username
  %p{style: "margin: 0 0 10px 0;"}
    %strong Email: 
    %a{href: "mailto:#{email}"}= email
%p
  This user can now access the platform with these credentials.